Male terminalia (Fig. 16
A-D
): epandrium with ca. 17 setae near posterior and ventral margins per side. Surstylus with six peg-like prensisetae. Hypandrium with a pair of paramedian setae and pubescence medially. Paramere with seven sensilla medially and pubescence distally. Aedeagus with pubescence ventrally.
